{"tid":1359703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大文豪fb話馮驊提議縮短投票時間","createTime":"2019-07-24T07:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T09:07:11.000Z","uid":167548,"like":8,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"584f0419923b967ec876986b5b412b2a7a206349","tid":1359703,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:49:18.000Z","msg":"【2016遺失選民登記冊調查】<br />\n成個調查點遺失查唔到，無上報又唔評論有無失職，偏偏馮驊係報告建議「因為監運選舉物資人數不足，會再諮詢縮短投票時間」。<br />\n喂人手不足就去請人輪班做，而唔係剝奪選民投票權力！而且2018年已經做過公眾諮詢，當時除咗保皇黨，絕大部分意見係不同意縮短投票時間。馮驊係咪要與民為敵到呢個地步？<br />\n#呢個建議簡直痴線<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2gEZQcw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2gEZQcw.jpg&h=cbfa6519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jeremytammanho/?__tn__=kC-R&amp;eid=ARAgBWQDWeyomVCPrhHu77FiLQwdyFNPJDW5lCsSaN3SlLhu9t6wz0Kj-iIr2MKBP5kwBLNiAq8MUrlS&amp;hc_ref=ARQ1g7gGWCJ9k9Pep7T2B6j73H6YjEgPZbBVmJ9bvFelW42G2M-vWiSZPlyGxM1wENI&amp;fref=nf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjeremytammanho%2F%3F__tn__%3DkC-R%26eid%3DARAgBWQDWeyomVCPrhHu77FiLQwdyFNPJDW5lCsSaN3SlLhu9t6wz0Kj-iIr2MKBP5kwBLNiAq8MUrlS%26hc_ref%3DARQ1g7gGWCJ9k9Pep7T2B6j73H6YjEgPZbBVmJ9bvFelW42G2M-vWiSZPlyGxM1wENI%26fref%3Dnf&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTewogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=946edaa6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jeremytammanho/?__tn__=kC-R&amp;eid=ARAgBWQDWeyomVCPrhHu77FiLQwdyFNPJDW5lCsSaN3SlLhu9t6wz0Kj-iIr2MKBP5kwBLNiAq8MUrlS&amp;hc_ref=ARQ1g7gGWCJ9k9Pep7T2B6j73H6YjEgPZbBVmJ9bvFelW42G2M-vWiSZPlyGxM1wENI&amp;fref=nf</a>"},{"pid":"32eda74b1adfe4c2517a0d181be91d0d0349092d","tid":1359703,"uid":167548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:49:43.000Z","msg":"DLLM&nbsp;馮驊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c6ee4237620ba0beb87a7d70cca952cb060c039","tid":1359703,"uid":237733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:4